{
  "message": "revert: remove fixture expansions with incompatible schemas\n\nThe added test cases use field schemas that the harness doesn't support.\nReverting until harness can be updated:\n\n- iter_differential_cases: multi-operand, external loop, seek/reset ops\n- rng_differential_cases: distribution, shuffle, choice ops\n- runtime_policy_adversarial: clamping and injection edge cases\n\nThese cases define useful test coverage but require harness changes.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
